{"tid":303583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[習總巡港]八鄉少年警訊應689謝犯罪率新低 盧偉聰:沒有內地公安支持不可能","createTime":"2017-06-30T09:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T17:13:51.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e6a07f8f7da189fc24465883ddf8115e7e7bf3","tid":303583,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1339187_1_L_20170630145336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1339187_1_L_20170630145336.jpg&h=68863729&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1339187-20170630.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1339187-20170630.htm&d=pfJr2N3EbyKllZWmyWlzgJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=262048e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1339187-20170630.htm&h=0fc31b44\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1339187-20170630.htm</a><br />\n盧偉聰稱感謝內地公安支持　如沒支持不可能有低犯罪率<br />\n2017-06-30 HKT 14:32<br />\n國家主席習近平早上參觀元朗少年警訊永久活動中心，行政長官梁振英和警務處處長盧偉聰陪同參觀，期間盧偉聰向習近平表示，感謝內地公安的支持。<br />\n<br />\n習近平參觀期間，梁振英提示盧偉聰向習近平介紹本港的罪案情況，盧偉聰說，現在是1978年以來，犯罪率最低的一年。<br />\n<br />\n習近平說，整體社會情況複雜起來、人口也是多起來，犯罪率反而要下降。盧偉聰隨即說，要感謝內地公安部隊的支持，如果沒有他們的支持，不可能有低犯罪率，習近平則說多多努力。<br />\n<br />\n有少年警訊成員向習近平介紹計劃內容，習近平了解參與計劃的年齡要求，又指他們學到很多在學校學不到的東西。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/police-13_IQyVm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpolice-13_IQyVm_1200x0.png&h=63d3565a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5-%E5%90%91%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%B8%AF%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2586%2592%25E7%259B%25AE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258A%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%2F&d=pfJr2N3EbyKllZWmyWlzgJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d31e8c66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2586%2592%25E7%259B%25AE%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E5%2590%2591%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258A%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2589%25B5%25E6%2596%25B0%25E4%25BD%258E-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E5%2581%2589%25E8%2581%25B0-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2583%25BD%2F&h=f1a40a44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%86%92%E7%9B%AE%E4%B8%80%E5%93%A5-%E5%90%91%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A%E6%B8%AF%E7%8A%AF%E7%BD%AA%E7%8E%87%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E7%9B%A7%E5%81%89%E8%81%B0-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD/</a><br />\n【醒目一哥】向習近平報告港犯罪率創新低　盧偉聰：沒有公安支持，我們不可能<br />\n2017/6/30 &mdash; 14:08<br />\n國家主席習近平訪港第二日，他在特首梁振英、警務處處長盧偉聰等人的陪同下，參觀了少年警訊活動中心。期間盧偉聰向習近平報告，稱香港犯罪率跌至1978年以來新低，他表示：「要感謝內地公安部隊的支持，沒有他們支持，我們不可能。」<br />\n<br />\n習近平今早到石崗軍營檢閱解放軍駐港部隊，之後即來到八鄉參觀少年警訊永久活動中心暨青少年綜合訓練營。他聽取少年警訊成員簡介訓練營設施等，然後觀看營內正在進行的領導才能及體能訓練，並與少年警訊成員交談及大合照。<br />\n<br />\n在參觀期間，梁振英叫盧偉聰向習近平交代香港犯罪率情況，盧偉聰即說道：「現在我們的犯罪率是1978年以來最低的一年。」習近平指出香港社會情況變得複雜，人口亦愈來愈多，但犯罪率反而有所下降。盧偉聰答道：「要感謝內地公安部隊的支持，沒有他們支持，我們不可能。」<br />\n<br />\n習近平夫人彭麗媛今早則在特首夫人梁唐青儀、勞福局局長蕭偉強、社署署長葉文娟等人陪同下，到黃竹坑的一間安老院探望長者。她參觀了院內住宿設施及探訪院友，又向負責護士了解院友日常的生活情況。結束探訪前，她向中心致送一部智能健康一體機及一部電視機。"},{"pid":"70a7ecbdbc883674dc0dffa9637f5e1cea2064f6","tid":303583,"uid":26721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"多謝佢地落埋黎幫手捉人返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20316bcc01bc0597b93b5e03e8372a3b340cce8e","tid":303583,"uid":60896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:11:38.000Z","msg":"你老母第一張圖殘體黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab7659264c1cebddd3899e4ff211506e17654bd","tid":303583,"uid":27215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"因為黑警唔做野囉"},{"pid":"8de0d3e4820280788629e96f2aea2e426e0b3d08","tid":303583,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母第一張圖殘體黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習近平龜兒子"},{"pid":"932392b620e087a79576b15ec35b9637f4d72ee4","tid":303583,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:21:07.000Z","msg":"關公安乜撚野事<br />\n公安係香港執法咩？<br />\n定係承認支那好多專才來港？"},{"pid":"d4c10f5725aa7ea9aa9073bad776db25850ba494","tid":303583,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T10:23:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母第一張圖殘體黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾雜種睇"},{"pid":"993060f87781d0d1155774ab5ee6a2248d7d7722","tid":303583,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"rep